Name:           perl-Set-Tiny
Version:        0.02
#Release:        1%{?dist}
Release:        0.1%{?dist}
Summary:        Simple sets of strings
License:        GPL+ or Artistic
Group:          Development/Libraries
URL:            http://search.cpan.org/dist/Set-Tiny/
#Source0:        http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/T/TR/TRENDELS/Set-Tiny-%{version}.tar.gz
